#: ../../source/detailed_guide/config.md:1
msgid "配置文件说明"
msgstr "Configuration file description"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/config.md:3
msgid "`.env` 文件"
msgstr "`.env` file"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/config.md:5
msgid ""
"`.env` 用于存放环境变量，本框架主要读取日志配置与 Langfuse 配置。你可以在项目的工作目录创建 "
"`.env`，也可以直接通过系统环境变量覆盖。"
msgstr ""
"`.env` is used to store environment variables. This framework primarily "
"reads log configuration and Langfuse configuration. You can create `.env` in"
" the project's working directory, or you can directly override it through "
"system environment variables."

