#: ../../source/detailed_guide/config.md:89
msgid "加载和使用"
msgstr "Loading and Usage"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/config.md:103
msgid "最佳实践"
msgstr "Best Practices"

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/config.md:105
msgid "**多密钥负载均衡**：同一模型配置多个 key，避免单 key 限流。"
msgstr ""
"**Multi-key load balancing**: Configure multiple keys for the same model to "
"avoid single key rate limiting."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/config.md:106
msgid ""
"**按模型调整限流**：高成本模型设置更保守的 `rate_limit_capacity` 与 `rate_limit_refill_rate`。"
msgstr ""
"**Adjust rate limiting by model**: Set more conservative "
"`rate_limit_capacity` and `rate_limit_refill_rate` for high-cost models."

#: ../../source/detailed_guide/config.md:107
msgid "**避免重复 `model_name`**：同一 provider 内的 `model_name` 将作为索引键，重复会覆盖。"
msgstr ""
"**Avoid duplicate `model_name`**: The `model_name` within the same provider "
"will be used as the index key, duplicates will be overwritten."

